{"tid":611691,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"CSGO: Zotac搞個比賽點解可以搞得咁廢","createTime":"2018-03-31T09:30:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T09:44:37.000Z","uid":159249,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fe6190a97ed7224f46cab30badae224a18143989","tid":611691,"uid":159249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T09:30:59.000Z","msg":"先唔講佢地搞比賽但每隊都提供唔到Ser, 一係就爆choke.結果最後13場比賽 得3場係開到.<br />\n但重點係想講番班垃圾admin既判斷力<br />\n首先呢個係香港區資格賽<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/171616_5d33cc5002c73af6b4ebbaa103fd79bd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F171616_5d33cc5002c73af6b4ebbaa103fd79bd.png&h=886b3c59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就有隊中國職業隊(Precious Genius)落左來報香港區打比賽,咁當然引起大把人不滿,跟住就好多人同admin投訴,指出<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/171927_6250c08a8a296d1dab68799207db58b8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F171927_6250c08a8a296d1dab68799207db58b8.png&h=986a1b2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但個admin就話已經核對晒身份證,確保係全香港人既隊伍,而Precious Genius都有人發言話佢地有3個隊員係香港人<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/172048_d991e316a198058e2374c70be4b2f56c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F172048_d991e316a198058e2374c70be4b2f56c.png&h=2e80628e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/172055_f3e9d5641757436c9e2c59a0930bb071.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F172055_f3e9d5641757436c9e2c59a0930bb071.png&h=f36390b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係想知佢地除左Shun-Hei Ho, Man-Ho Yip 佢地隊仲有邊個夠資格打香港區比賽??<br />\n<br />\n真係好唔合理,見到zotac既處事能力.個個都係咁指出個問題. 但admin仍然無視 由得佢地繼續打比賽<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/172249_2643bdca33d619955eb9191b47d9b892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F172249_2643bdca33d619955eb9191b47d9b892.png&h=94f9d154&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隊中國隊打唔掂南亞區既人要落來香港區搵食,打唔掂就咪學人組職業隊<br />\n同埋Zotac好心就專心出顯卡算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 學咩人搞比賽, Server 廢, admin又廢.<br />\n一早知香港電競希望很細, 難得有個比賽.但沒諗到連Zotac呢種大公司都搞到成舊垃圾咁.<br />\n見到真係得啖笑<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/173055_3fccaf39018582b617d0f9ab23eaecef.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F173055_3fccaf39018582b617d0f9ab23eaecef.png&h=59d1a6f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96663018d6cb966329417de15cf2bdcf59015947","tid":611691,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T09:38:00.000Z","msg":"廢game"},{"pid":"ab8c2646667d5fc9b87fdf0f579c3b28ddcd6f81","tid":611691,"uid":179672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96663018d6cb966329417de15cf2bdcf59015947","tid":611691,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T09:38:00.000Z","msg":"廢game"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T09:44:37.000Z","msg":"玩左咁多年<br />\n我都覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁認真做乜<br />\n外國比賽班友都係開外掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}